00:01:31.490 --> 00:01:34.440 align:middle line:90%


00:01:34.440 --> 00:01:37.380 align:middle line:84%
Until recently, the idea of
not being able to eat bread

00:01:37.380 --> 00:01:40.440 align:middle line:84%
was crazy, but
the wheat products

00:01:40.440 --> 00:01:42.210 align:middle line:84%
