grocery stores

00:01:42.210 --> 00:01:45.450 align:middle line:84%
are more difficult to
digest, and it's all thanks

00:01:45.450 --> 00:01:48.760 align:middle line:90%
to this thing called gluten.

00:01:48.760 --> 00:01:52.020 align:middle line:84%
>> Gluten is essentially
these two kinds of proteins,

00:01:52.020 --> 00:01:57.200 align:middle line:84%
