nausea, exhaustion.

00:02:17.850 --> 00:02:21.690 align:middle line:84%
It's like my body is trying
to fight off the bread.

00:02:21.690 --> 00:02:24.690 align:middle line:84%
Since I live in the
bread basket of America,

00:02:24.690 --> 00:02:28.220 align:middle line:84%
