00:03:03.770 --> 00:03:09.380 align:middle line:84%
>> Gluten intolerance has
become this enormous obsession.

00:03:09.380 --> 00:03:13.250 align:middle line:84%
Gluten free advertisement
on a product

00:03:13.250 --> 00:03:15.260 align:middle line:84%
is one of the most
effective ways

00:03:15.260 --> 00:03:19.030 align:middle line:90%
