00:03:19.030 --> 00:03:21.710 align:middle line:84%
When we see gluten
free, that connotes

00:03:21.710 --> 00:03:23.600 align:middle line:90%
healthy in the grocery store.

00:03:23.600 --> 00:03:25.190 align:middle line:84%
