necessarily the case,

00:03:25.190 --> 00:03:29.940 align:middle line:84%
because there's a lot of really
cruddy gluten free products.

00:03:29.940 --> 00:03:31.350 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes, absolutely.

00:03:31.350 --> 00:03:32.760 align:middle line:90%
