00:04:01.225 --> 00:04:04.270 align:middle line:84%
>> It could all be
in your head, yes.

00:04:04.270 --> 00:04:05.170 align:middle line:90%
It's a possibility.

00:04:05.170 --> 00:04:06.820 align:middle line:90%
>> OK, great.

00:04:06.820 --> 00:04:10.870 align:middle line:84%
