increased, too.

00:04:53.560 --> 00:04:55.720 align:middle line:84%
So maybe gluten
tolerance is part

00:04:55.720 --> 00:04:59.200 align:middle line:84%
of a bigger story about
how our immune systems just

00:04:59.200 --> 00:05:00.440 align:middle line:90%
don't work like they used to.

00:05:00.440 --> 00:05:03.062 align:middle line:90%


