wanted to find a real wheat

00:05:36.990 --> 00:05:40.230 align:middle line:84%
bread I could eat,
maybe I should just

00:05:40.230 --> 00:05:43.848 align:middle line:90%
start at the beginning.

00:05:43.848 --> 00:05:46.940 align:middle line:84%
>> There are a lot of just
so stories about the origin

00:05:46.940 --> 00:05:47.740 align:middle line:90%
of bread.

00:05:47.740 --> 00:05:55.410 align:middle line:90%


00:05:55.410 --> 00:05:59.030 align:middle line:84%
It's not like there's
an aha moment where

00:05:59.030 --> 00:06:01.520 align:middle line:84%
