00:06:01.520 --> 00:06:03.500 align:middle line:84%
and someone says, oh,
I have risen bread.

00:06:03.500 --> 00:06:06.560 align:middle line:84%
You know, this is
a long, let's say,

00:06:06.560 --> 00:06:10.130 align:middle line:84%
spectrum of degrees until you
get to a really poofy loaf

00:06:10.130 --> 00:06:12.870 align:middle line:90%
like we have.

00:06:12.870 --> 00:06:16.340 align:middle line:84%
