more complicated,

00:08:23.750 --> 00:08:24.980 align:middle line:90%
and it's a premium product.

00:08:24.980 --> 00:08:26.860 align:middle line:90%
There's a specialty product.

00:08:26.860 --> 00:08:29.600 align:middle line:84%
