that whole wheat wasn't

00:14:43.800 --> 00:14:45.090 align:middle line:90%
as whole as I thought it was.

00:14:45.090 --> 00:14:47.220 align:middle line:84%
In fact, I still
wasn't quite sure

00:14:47.220 --> 00:14:49.516 align:middle line:84%
what the whole
wheat label meant.

00:14:49.516 --> 00:14:54.730 align:middle line:84%
>> The FDA allows for whole
wheat statements of health

00:14:54.730 --> 00:14:59.860 align:middle line:84%
