00:15:08.650 --> 00:15:11.170 align:middle line:84%
You're still losing a
lot of those nutrients.

00:15:11.170 --> 00:15:14.110 align:middle line:84%
So if you go to the store and
you buy a loaf of bread that

00:15:14.110 --> 00:15:17.490 align:middle line:84%
