00:17:14.050 --> 00:17:17.280 align:middle line:84%
They could boast about the fact
that they had extra nutrients

00:17:17.280 --> 00:17:19.020 align:middle line:84%
in this food,
nutrients, of course,

00:17:19.020 --> 00:17:20.809 align:middle line:84%
that they had taken
