00:21:19.300 --> 00:21:21.550 align:middle line:90%
So how did this change?

00:21:21.550 --> 00:21:25.050 align:middle line:84%
>> About 100 years ago,
the great Louis Pasteur--

00:21:25.050 --> 00:21:27.300 align:middle line:90%
